snippet.textDisplay: "COVID-19 and its resulting illness" implies a causal-linear relationship between COVID-19 and COVID-19, which is unambiguous and untrue. COVID-19 is the name of the disease (coronavirus disease 2019). It doesn't cause the illness, as diseases don't cause themselves. SARS-CoV2 is the pathogen which causes the disease (severe acute respiratory syndrome-related coronavirus #2). I like your message nonetheless.
snippet.textOriginal: "COVID-19 and its resulting illness" implies a causal-linear relationship between COVID-19 and COVID-19, which is unambiguous and untrue. COVID-19 is the name of the disease (coronavirus disease 2019). It doesn't cause the illness, as diseases don't cause themselves. SARS-CoV2 is the pathogen which causes the disease (severe acute respiratory syndrome-related coronavirus #2). I like your message nonetheless.
